        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-200 mb-2">Submit a task</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">POST to <code class="text-violet-400 text-xs">/v1/tasks</code> with the task type and input. Or use the TypeScript / Python SDK.</p>
