    <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm text-center mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">You could wire up each provider yourself. Here's what you'd need to build.</p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      {[
        {
          title: "Unified task schema",
          desc: "One input/output format across 10 task types. No learning 10 different API schemas.",
          icon: "📐",
        },
        {
          title: "Automatic routing",
